'''中亚足球联合会'''（[[英语|英语]]：'''Central Asian Football Association'''，简称CAFA）<ref>{{cite web|title=اتحادیه فوتبال آسیای مرکزی ایجاد شد|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/persian/afghanistan/2015/02/150221_zs_central_asian_football_association|publisher=BBC|accessdate=22 February 2015|date=22 February 2015|language=fa|archive-date=2015-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150223133832/http://www.bbc.co.uk/persian/afghanistan/2015/02/150221_zs_central_asian_football_association|dead-url=no}}</ref>是一个由中亚各足球成员协会组成足球机构，也是亚足联分支机构。

2014年7月，中亚足球联合会为[[亚洲足球联合会|亚洲足球联合会]]批准成立，并在2015年1月在[[2015年亚洲杯足球赛|亚洲杯]]期间举行特别会议。<ref>{{cite web|title='Central Zone' gets thumbs up from Tajikistan|url=http://www.the-afc.com/en/about-afc/afc-committees/1127-executive-committee/28784-central-zone-gets-thumbs-up-from-tajikistan.html|publisher=The AFC|accessdate=10 June 2014|date=10 June 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140612013350/http://www.the-afc.com/en/about-afc/afc-committees/1127-executive-committee/28784-central-zone-gets-thumbs-up-from-tajikistan.html|archivedate=2014年6月12日}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=AFC adds a fifth zone as Extraordinary Congress approves amendments to AFC Statutes|url=http://www.the-afc.com/executive-committee/afc-adds-a-fifth-zone-as-extraordinary-congress-approves-amendments-to-afc|publisher=The AFC|accessdate=9 January 2015|date=12 January 2015|archive-date=2017-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170830171125/http://www.the-afc.com/executive-committee/afc-adds-a-fifth-zone-as-extraordinary-congress-approves-amendments-to-afc|dead-url=no}}</ref>最终，中亚足球联合会将被接纳为亚足联执行委员会一部分。

由于与[[西亚足球协会|西亚足球联合会]]其他成员存在各种纠纷，[[伊朗足球协会|伊朗足球协会]]决定牵头成立中亚足球联合会。据报道亚足联主席[[萨尔曼|萨尔曼]]获得了新成立的区域足球联合会的政治上的支持。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Warshaw|first1=Andrew|title=Shaikh Salman flexes his political muscle to brush aside Prince Ali|url=http://www.insideworldfootball.com/world-football/asia/14820-shaikh-salman-flexes-his-political-muscle-to-brush-aside-prince-ali|publisher=InsideWorldFootball.com|accessdate=10 June 2014|date=10 June 2014|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304032416/http://www.insideworldfootball.com/world-football/asia/14820-shaikh-salman-flexes-his-political-muscle-to-brush-aside-prince-ali|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==历史==
2014年5月10日，六个成员协会代表与亚洲足球联合会主席萨尔曼会见，讨论成立新的亚洲足球区域的可能性。在伊朗跟阿富汗的倡议下，代表团受到亚洲足球联合会主席的邀请。<ref>{{cite web|title=Central Asians meet Sheikh Salman to create CAFA|url=http://aff.org.af/english/central-asians-meet-sheikh-salman-to-create-cafa/|publisher=aff.org.af|accessdate=29 October 2014|date=17 May 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141029194753/http://aff.org.af/english/central-asians-meet-sheikh-salman-to-create-cafa/|archivedate=2014年10月29日}}</ref>2014年6月9日，亚足联在巴西圣保罗召开特别大会，新区域的成立这一计划在大会上得到批准。<ref>{{cite web|title=Sheikh Salman Wins Bitter Battle to End Prince Ali's FIFA Vice-Presidency|url=http://www.worldfootballinsider.com/Story.aspx?id=37037|publisher=worldfootballinsider.com|accessdate=29 October 2014|format=10 June 2014|archive-date=2014-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141029191636/http://www.worldfootballinsider.com/Story.aspx?id=37037|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=AFC president to resume FIFA Vice Presidency|url=http://www.goal.com/en-sg/news/3952/asia/2014/06/11/4873346/afc-president-to-assume-fifa-vice-presidency|publisher=goal.com|accessdate=29 October 2014|date=11 June 2014|archive-date=2019-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190512060913/https://www.goal.com/en-sg/news/3952/asia/2014/06/11/4873346/afc-president-to-assume-fifa-vice-presidency|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==中亚足球联合会锦标赛==
[[阿富汗足球协会|阿富汗足球协会]]秘书长Seyed Reza Aghazadeh在2015年2月宣布，第一届中亚足球联合会锦标赛将可能在2016年举办。<ref>{{cite web|title=Last Afghanistan championship|url=http://www.goalnepal.com/news.php?id=23372/|publisher=Goal Nepal|accessdate=23 February 2015|date=23 February 2015|archive-date=2016-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160320205606/http://www.goalnepal.com/news.php?id=23372%2F|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.goal.com/en-india/news/2696/indian-national-team/2015/02/26/9256272/afghanistan-to-play-saff-championship-for-the-last-time-in |title=Afghanistan to play SAFF Championship for the last time in 2015 |accessdate=2015-10-01 |archive-date=2017-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170910115858/http://www.goal.com/en-india/news/2696/indian-national-team/2015/02/26/9256272/afghanistan-to-play-saff-championship-for-the-last-time-in |dead-url=no }}</ref>第一届中亚足球联合会15岁以下锦标赛于2015年3月23日在日本东京开幕。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://afghanistantimes.af/cafa-championship-afghan-u-15-football-squad-off-to-japan/ |title=CAFA championship: Afghan U-15 football squad off to Japan |accessdate=2015-10-01 |archive-date=2020-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201025100843/http://www.afghanistantimes.af/cafa-championship-afghan-u-15-football-squad-off-to-japan/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

